prontoloadtestingpkg

Class ProntoJourney

  • java.lang.Object
    • prontoloadtestingpkg.ProntoJourney
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProntoJourney1

    public abstract class ProntoJourney
extends java.lang.Object
    The pronto journey is an abstract class that. It has a defined constructor to pass in the winium drover and arrays of test data. It provides base method to obtain arrays of test data, as well as providing a random access lookup to get a random entry. It also has a delay method for holding up the execution of any specific journey.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Rob Allan DX Solutions
